A renowned Nollywood actor, Kayode Odumosu, is dead. It was gathered that he died at about 12.00pm on Sunday, March 1, 2020, after a brief illness.
Pa Kasumu was a household name in the Yoruba movie industry until he came down with Biventricular Heart Failure in 2013. The 67-year-old actor, who featured in several movies in his heyday, has been off the public radar in the past seven years.

















			
